    <item>
      <title>加拿大投资数百万美元建设芯片网络，美国紧随其后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-invests-millions-to-build-chip-network-as-us-races-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将在五年内投资 1.2 亿加元（8820 万美元）建设国家芯片网络，与此同时，要求政府采取更多措施支持其落后的半导体行业的呼声越来越高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-invests-millions-to-build-chip-network-as-us-races-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 17:35:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LME 第二季度交易量飙升至 10 年来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/lme-second-quarter-trading-volumes-surge-to-a-10-year-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所 (LME) 交易量第二季度飙升 27%，达到十年来的最高水平，其中 LME 镍合约的大幅上涨引领其主要金属交易活动上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/lme-second-quarter-trading-volumes-surge-to-a-10-year-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 17:28:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
